---
title: Carb Smart Dill Pickle Chicken Breasts Salad with Garlic Croutons and Dill Pickle Cream
description: Another chicken salad you say?! This isn't just any chicken salad. The dill pickle cream that gets dolloped on top livens up the plate while the garlic croutons add a gorgeous crunch to every bite!
